>&lt;/a>
&lt;/h5>&lt;p>&lt;!-- raw HTML omitted -->Relationship between Change Management, Configuration Management, Capacity Management and Release Management ～变更、配置、能力和发布管理之间的关系。&lt;!-- raw HTML omitted -->&lt;!-- raw HTML omitted -->&lt;a class="link" href="http://lh4.google.com/liuzh66/R3j6_oClhbI/AAAAAAAAAK4/U0FWq6YXMRk/fig3_1%5B4%5D" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
